    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your<strong> aubergine[s]</strong> in half, lengthways</p><p>Score the flesh in a criss-cross pattern, taking care not to cut through the skin</p><p>Rub the flesh with a drizzle of<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>scored</strong> <strong>aubergine halves </strong>to the reserved baking tray (use <strong>tin foil</strong> to avoid mess!) and put the tray in the oven for an initial 15 min</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1660661421820-x200.jpg",
