            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>tomato paste </strong>with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>in a bowl with<strong> </strong>2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato sauce</strong></p><p>Drain and pat your <strong>mozzarella</strong> dry with kitchen paper (squeeze as much liquid out as you can!) and tear into rough, bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1660661468114-x200.jpg",
