          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1660661468114-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the aubergine<strong> </strong>has slightly softened, remove the tray from the oven and top with the <strong>tomato sauce</strong>, then spread it out<strong> </strong>evenly with the back of a spoon and add the <strong>torn mozzarella</strong></p><p>Return the tray to the oven for 10-15 min or until the mozzarella is melted and golden – this is your <strong>roasted cheesy aubergine</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1660661480194-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1660661480194-x400.jpg",
