            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1660661486205-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad </strong>and pat dry with kitchen paper, then cut the <strong>remaining lemon </strong>into wedges</p><p>Serve the <strong>basil pesto beans </strong>over the <strong>salad </strong>with the <strong>roasted cheesy aubergine </strong>to the side</p><p>Crumble over the <strong>toasted flaked almonds </strong>and garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
